{"tid":702894,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"女朋友生日寫左首歌比佢，點知比佢屌鳩我","createTime":"2018-06-15T09:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T10:51:26.000Z","uid":31827,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"326524821daa1ef73a28d11c46707cd8b1eda360","tid":702894,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚係女朋友生日，咁我以為自己好醒啦，一早寫好首歌<br />\n（自學左一排結他，膽粗粗咁寫，仲以為係女都會鍾意）<br />\n<br />\n點知女朋友好似有啲面黑黑，我都心知不妙。雖然佢冇話唔鍾意，但係就間接咁話我首歌啲歌詞好俗。<br />\n<br />\n其實我只係想簡簡單單咁表達我對你既心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴晚唔開心左成晚，自己又寫左首歌，講述當刻既心情。<br />\n唱得唔好，只係想分享下心情，希望你睇到呢個post，知道我既心意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TueRHDsYW-s&amp;t=4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTueRHDsYW-s%26t%3D4s&d=DCzNlVhyL84GmMZ20lFm5Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=03d7c18c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TueRHDsYW-s&amp;t=4s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《任性》</span></span>（係講緊你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n愛如果是一首情歌<br />\n想讓你聽見<br />\n載著這些日子以來的思念<br />\n你卻說你不喜歡  感情盡顯<br />\n不用比喻的歌詞是難免庸俗一點<br />\n<br />\n微風落進了海洋深底<br />\n遺失了記憶中的你<br />\n夢在紛繞<br />\n沉入滄海裡<br />\n聲音擱淺在你的心<br />\n<br />\n害怕你愈走愈遠<br />\n無情的像葡公英<br />\n讓人受不了的脾氣<br />\n還會有誰答應<br />\n每次傷心還是要我<br />\n看你心情<br />\n可是 就是喜歡你<br />\n任性的你"},{"pid":"02bab097705fd0267eedfbad709e59bd1bc114b4","tid":702894,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"人地想收💎, 你就作首濕鳩歌<img 